# Jiggon Algorithm: Trend Rider
# Focuses heavily on aligning with the overall Moving Average trend
# and waits for MACD momentum to cross the zero line in the direction of the trend.

IF RSI < 70 AND MACD > 0 AND EMA_TREND == BULLISH THEN BUY
IF RSI > 30 AND MACD < 0 AND EMA_TREND == BEARISH THEN SELL
